FYI For those who are going to download this map and want to add it to your map list.
There is only one ramp in middle building leading to the second floor and i did that on purpose.

*Once your over the wall there is no going back you have to fight it out running through out floors and being careful what means of escape or routes you take not to forget once more there is only one ramp from middle building leading up to the second floor. please have fun, this is a Promotional map intended to promote the awareness of the clan hence why there is DNA banners.

I hope you enjoy please leave opinions in order so that i can make even better maps. 
                                   Thank You: Panda
